<HEADLINE> Uganda Denounces Rwanda for Breaking Agreements </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, June 11 (Xinhua) -- Uganda denounced that Rwanda has
broken various agreements, cease-fires and troop withdrawal from
Kisangani in the Democratic Republic of the Congo (DRC), James
Wapakabulo, chairman of the National Coordinations Committee on
