<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, June 11 (Xinhua) -- Ethiopian President Negaso
Gidada Sunday expressed his great sadness over the death of Syrian
President Hafez Al-Assad.
</P>
<P>
In his message of condolence to Bishir Assad, the son of the
late Syrian president, Negaso said the death of Assad is a great
loss not only to the Syrian people, but also to all who have
appreciated his immense contribution to the prosperity of Syria
and to durable peace in the Middle East.
</P>
<P>
He expressed his heartfelt sympathy for and condolences to the
Syrian people and all members of the bereaved family.
</P>
<P>
