<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, June 11 (Xinhua) -- Secretary-General of the Gulf
Cooperation Council (GCC) Jameel al-Hujailan on Sunday expressed
sorrow at the death of Syrian President Hafez al-Assad, wishing
Syria stable and prosperous.
</P>
<P>
Al-Hujailan said at the GCC headquarters in Saudi capital Riyadh
that the GCC Secretariat-General shares with the Arab nation the
sorrow and sadness over Assad's death.
</P>
<P>
