<P>
BAGHDAD, June 11 (Xinhua) -- Iraqi Vice President Taha Mohyiddin
Marouf will go to Syria to attend the funeral of late Syrian
President Hafez Al-Assad who died on Saturday of a heart attack,
Iraqi News Agency reported Sunday.
</P>
