who excel in computer applications, English language, and
international trade.
</P>
<P>
MeetChina.com, established by U.S. Business Network Inc. and
China's Ministry of Information Industry mainly focuses on finding
foreign importers for Chinese suppliers and listing prices for
thousands of toys, factory equipment and other goods. 
