<HEADLINE> Putin Blasts U.S. ABM Plan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
MOSCOW, June 11 (Xinhua) -- Russian President Vladimir Putin
on Sunday strongly denounced the U.S. plan to deploy a national
missile defense (NMD) system and urged Europe to support the
preservation of the 1972 Anti-Ballistic Missile (ABM) treaty.
