<HEADLINE> Daily Report on Quality of Air in Key Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The report, issued by the China Environmental Monitoring Center,
said that Beijing, Tianjin, Shenyang, Dalian, Changchun, Harbin,
Shanghai, Nanjing, Suzhou, Nantong, Hangzhou, Wenzhou, Fuzhou,
Jinan, Qingdao, Yantai, Zhengzhou, Wuhan, Guangzhou, Zhanjiang,
Nanning, Chongqing, Chengdu, Guiyang, Xi'an, Lanzhou, Xining,
