chairman of the NPC Standing Committee; Gao Dezhan, member of the
NPC Standing Committee and chairman of the NPC Agriculture and
Rural Affairs Committee; Xie Shijie, chairman of the Sichuan
Provincial People's Congress Standing Committee; Ren Keli,
chairman of the Henan Provincial People's Congress Standing
Committee; Li Laizhu and Nie Dajiang, members of the NPC Standing
Committee; Lu Congmin, deputy secretary-general of the NPC
Standing Committee; Yang Wenchang, vice foreign minister; and Wu
Wenchang, director of the NPC Chairman's Office.
